  m_Text: "By creating an account, I agree to the Terms of Use below.\n\n\r\rThe Walt Disney Company (Australia) Pty Limited collects personal information such as name, birth date and email address so we can provide you with access to My Disney and other Disney sites, and personalize the content and experience of those sites. We may disclose it to our service providers and other members of The Walt Disney Group (including overseas) in a manner consistent with the Australian Privacy Principles. For more information, including how to contact us, please read our Privacy Policy below. Please note that you do not have to provide your real name when registering."
